            <div class="SCXW242016415 BCX8">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">O que &eacute; Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Aberta?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta se baseia na articula&ccedil;&atilde;o dos diferentes atores do ecossistema de neg&oacute;cios, promovendo um modelo colaborativo que gera valor estrat&eacute;gico para a empresa. Seguindo a abordagem cl&aacute;ssica de H. </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">Chesbrough</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"> (2006), "a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; um paradigma que assume que as empresas podem e devem utilizar tanto ideias externas quanto internas, assim como caminhos internos e externos para alcan&ccedil;ar o mercado em seu desenvolvimento tecnol&oacute;gico".</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Essa abordagem sempre fez sentido, considerando que desde o in&iacute;cio de nossa hist&oacute;ria, desempenhamos um papel crucial em potencializar conex&otilde;es, aproximando empresas e universidades, por exemplo. Com o tempo, acumulamos experi&ecirc;ncias pr&aacute;ticas e implementamos ferramentas de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta desde 2011, amadurecendo nossa vis&atilde;o. Inicialmente focada em P&amp;D, a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta mediada por uma plataforma conectava empresas "demandantes" com atores "ofertantes", investigando o "O que fazer" e "Como fazer", fosse com usu&aacute;rios (p&uacute;blico-alvo) ou especialistas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">A Expans&atilde;o da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Aberta</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Hoje, a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta se expande para incluir uma atua&ccedil;&atilde;o em rede das organiza&ccedil;&otilde;es, envolvendo:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Processos de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">co-cria&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">;</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Modelos de neg&oacute;cio colaborativos;</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">L&oacute;gica de gera&ccedil;&atilde;o de valor compartilhado.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;<img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Imagem-1-artigo.png"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Evolu&ccedil;&atilde;o Junto com o Ecossistema</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Essa nova vis&atilde;o da inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta nos leva a imaginar uma empresa sem limita&ccedil;&otilde;es f&iacute;sicas, como uma membrana celular que permite trocas constantes entre os ambientes interno e externo. Essa "c&eacute;lula" est&aacute; imersa em um meio ambiente rico, potencializando e valorizando essas trocas com o ecossistema, maximizando conex&otilde;es e construindo estruturas e recursos compartilhados entre agentes internos e externos.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Implementando a Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Aberta</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Para implementar a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta, uma organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o deve compreender quest&otilde;es centrais:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list" start="1">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="21" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<h5 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Objetivos e Desafios</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></strong></h5>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle2 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="o" data-font="Courier New" data-listid="21" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="2">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Defini&ccedil;&atilde;o da vis&atilde;o de futuro, territ&oacute;rios de neg&oacute;cio e direcionadores estrat&eacute;gicos. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta permite uma mudan&ccedil;a de paradigma, passando de uma abordagem "baseada em problemas x focada em solu&ccedil;&otilde;es" para uma "orientada por desafios". Encarar os desafios &eacute; poss&iacute;vel por meio da </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">co-constru&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"> de solu&ccedil;&otilde;es, ouvindo e engajando outros agentes.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list" start="2">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="21" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<h5 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Atores</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></strong></h5>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle2 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="o" data-font="Courier New" data-listid="21" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="2">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Compreens&atilde;o do ecossistema de neg&oacute;cios, mapeamento dos atores, compet&ecirc;ncias e tecnologias. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta se faz em rede, potencializando rela&ccedil;&otilde;es com m&uacute;ltiplos stakeholders e trocando conhecimento de forma multidirecional.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list" start="3">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="21" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<h5 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Formas e Mecanismos de Intera&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></strong></h5>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle2 SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="o" data-font="Courier New" data-listid="21" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="2">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Desenho dos modelos de intera&ccedil;&atilde;o, colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o e parceria conforme as diretrizes e desafios do neg&oacute;cio. Existem diversas formas/mecanismos de intera&ccedil;&atilde;o, e o objetivo &eacute; maximizar as "frentes de ataque" com iniciativas diversificadas de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta de forma estrat&eacute;gica.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="SCXW242016415 BCX8">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">A Jornada da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Aberta</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A jornada da inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta n&atilde;o deve ser restrita a exemplos, mas sim maximizada:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Imagem3-1024x454.png" width="713" height="316">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Desafio: Como gerar valor a partir dessa conex&atilde;o?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de onde est&atilde;o os conhecimentos, como se conectar, e compreender quais capacidades, recursos ou outros ativos faltam internamente ou podem ser oferecidos ao mercado.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Solu&ccedil;&atilde;o com a Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Aberta:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Busca de complementaridade estrat&eacute;gica com ciclos acelerados de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, agregando novos conhecimentos de m&uacute;ltiplos parceiros em cada fase e aplicados em solu&ccedil;&otilde;es. Esses ciclos curtos s&atilde;o sustentados por rela&ccedil;&otilde;es de longo prazo, multiplicando o valor gerado e compartilhado entre todos os envolvidos.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Imagem1-1024x535.png" width="681" height="356"></span></p>
</div>
<h3 class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">Tempo</h3>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o desempenha um papel chave, atuando como catalisadora de conex&otilde;es, <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">co-cria&ccedil;&atilde;o</span> e gera&ccedil;&atilde;o de valor. Isso permite acelerar a produ&ccedil;&atilde;o de inova&ccedil;&otilde;es com potencial de gerar impacto positivo para a empresa, seus parceiros e a sociedade. Para enfrentar desafios, a empresa deve propor a&ccedil;&otilde;es transversais (internas/externas) de abertura e <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">co-cria&ccedil;&atilde;o</span>, sempre alinhadas ao planejamento <span class="NormalTextRun CommentStart CommentHighlightPipeRestV2 CommentHighlightRest SCXW242016415 BCX8">estrat&eacute;gico</span><span class="NormalTextRun CommentHighlightPipeRestV2 SCXW242016415 BCX8">.</span></span></span></span></p>
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8">Contexto Global e Futuro da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Aberta</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Conforme a Harvard Business Review destacou em "</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">Why</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">Now</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">Is</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW242016415 BCX8">the</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"> Time for Open Innovation" (2020), as empresas est&atilde;o buscando abordagens colaborativas e voltando-se para a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta para envolver e fortalecer todos os envolvidos. Isso permite gerar solu&ccedil;&otilde;es criativas e inesperadas, com conhecimento e tecnologia desenvolvidos em uma velocidade sem precedentes. A colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o continuar&aacute; sendo crucial, expandindo o espa&ccedil;o para a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de valor por meio de novas parcerias e rela&ccedil;&otilde;es de longo prazo.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242016415 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Durante a pandemia, as formas de colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o foram reinventadas, aproximando e escalando parcerias a n&iacute;vel global. Esperamos que os resultados positivos dessas mudan&ccedil;as sejam absorvidos e multiplicados no longo prazo. Portanto, reflita sobre o potencial da inova&ccedil;&atilde;o aberta para sua organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242016415 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW242016415 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW204466500 BCX8">
<h3>Sobre a Avantt.i&nbsp;</h3>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A Avantt.i &eacute; uma plataforma de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o desenvolvida pela Inventta, para gestores de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o e gerentes de projeto.</p>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Com m&oacute;dulos de intra, open e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio, oferecemos uma vis&atilde;o completa da Gest&atilde;o da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o para alavancar suas iniciativas.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Vis&atilde;o global e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio: </strong>Atrav&eacute;s da consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, a Avantt.i ajuda a identificar os principais projetos e avan&ccedil;ar com assertividade. Tudo em uma &uacute;nica plataforma.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Programa de intra: </strong>Crie desafios e obtenha participa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos colaboradores. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o vira rotina e voc&ecirc; impulsiona a cultura de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o na empresa.</li>
<li><strong>Open Innovation:</strong> Chame startups e parceiros para desafios, gerencie parceria na plataforma e tenha acesso a mais de 23.000 startups na nossa base.</li>
<li><strong>M&eacute;tricas Acion&aacute;veis: </strong>Influencie a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o a investir em esfor&ccedil;os de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o com base em m&eacute;tricas claras e acion&aacute;veis. Me&ccedil;a resultados dos projetos e comunique o sucesso das iniciativas</li>
<li><strong>Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Integrada e Transparente: </strong>Gerencie projetos de diferentes esteiras e horizontes, com colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o de parceiros e equipe, visualizando o portf&oacute;lio globalmente.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Engajamento com Conhecimento: </strong>Transforme a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o em h&aacute;bito com trilhas de conhecimento e mentorias dispon&iacute;veis ao longo da jornada.&nbsp;<br><br>Conhe&ccedil;a <a href="https://materiais.avanttinovacao.com.br/avantti-inovacao-primeiro-passo">aqui</a>, solicite uma demonstra&ccedil;&atilde;o guiada e teste gr&aacute;tis.<a href="https://materiais.avanttinovacao.com.br/avantti-inovacao-primeiro-passo"><span class="EOP SCXW195930854 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img src="https://d335luupugsy2.cloudfront.net/cms/files/808420/1720784635/$63vucuqtfj9" width="673" height="448"></span></a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
